                    of Non-Fungible Tokens (Biddings), more popularly referred to as
                    ‘Crypto Collectibles.’ The world of Biddings is growing rapidly.
                </p>
                <p class="bid-now">Bidding Price: <span>$@Model.Prise</span></p>
                <div class="bid-form">
                    <p>Bid Now</p>
                    <p>Bid Amount: Minimum Bid $@Model.Prise</p>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="$00.00" />
                    <button type="submit">Place Bid</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
